cat << EOF
gnormalize decodes the MP3/MP4/MPC/OGG/FLAC file to WAV, then
normalizes the WAV to a targeted volume level and re-encodes it.
Moreover, gnormalize can extract Audio CD track and output as various
popular audio formats (MP3, MP4, MPC, OGG, FLAC, WAV) with fast speed
and high quality. gnormalize can also convert audio format between
MP3, MP4, MPC, OGG and FLAC with high fidelity, which meets your
need to play and collect audio files. It can change the encoding
and Metadata (tag) properties of final normalized files.
EOF
